 [55.5, 702.0, 701.6, 722.8]}, {"text": "9,307", "bbox": [803.3, 702.0, 850.2, 722.8]}, {"text": "12,822", "bbox": [952.3, 702.0, 1009.6, 722.8]}, {"text": "21,266", "bbox": [1112.5, 702.0, 1169.8, 722.8]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [718.7, 728.1, 729.1, 748.9]}, {"text": "147,690", "bbox": [782.4, 728.1, 850.2, 748.9]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [878.1, 728.1, 888.5, 748.9]}, {"text": "146,222", "bbox": [941.9, 728.1, 1009.6, 748.9]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [1037.5, 728.1, 1048.0, 748.9]}, {"text": "528,287", "bbox": [1102.0, 728.1, 1169.8, 748.9]}, {"text": "We completed our acquisition of Borgata on August 1, 2016 and therefore began to consolidate Borgata beginning on that date.", "bbox": [107.3, 780.7, 1181.9, 801.5]}, {"text": "Prior thereto our 50% ownership interest in Borgata was accounted for under the equity method.", "bbox": [56.3, 804.6, 859.1, 825.5]}, {"text": "In 2018, our share of CityCenter’s operating results, including certain basis difference adjustments, was $138 million compared", "bbox": [107.3, 852.6, 1181.8, 873.4]}, {"text": "to $133 million in 2017, primarily due to a $12 million gain on the sale of Mandarin Oriental that we recognized in 2018 related to the", "bbox": [56.3, 876.5, 1181.7, 897.4]}, {"text": "reversal of basis differences in excess of our share of the loss recorded by CityCenter. At Aria, casino revenues decreased 2% in 2018", "bbox": [56.3, 900.5, 1181.7, 921.3]}, {"text": "compared to 2017 due to an increase in incentives and a decrease in table games hold. CityCenter’s non-casino revenues increased 7%", "bbox": [56.3, 924.5, 1181.7, 945.3]}, {"text": "in 2018 compared to 2017 primarily related to an increase in food and beverage revenue due in part to an increase in restaurant", "bbox": [56.3, 948.4, 1181.7, 969.3]}, {"text": "revenues and an increase in catering and banquets during the year.", "bbox": [56.3, 972.4, 609.0, 993.2]}, {"text": "In 2017, our share of CityCenter’s operating results, including certain basis difference adjustments, was $133 million compared", "bbox": [107.3, 1020.3, 1181.8, 1041.2]}, {"text": "to $446 million in 2016, primarily due to our $401 million share of a gain recognized by CityCenter on the sale of Crystals and the", "bbox": [56.3, 1044.3, 1181.7, 1065.1]}, {"text": "corresponding reversal of certain basis differences in 2016. At Aria, casino revenues increased 11% in 2017 compared to 2016 due to", "bbox": [56.3, 1068.2, 1181.7, 1089.1]}, {"text": "an increase in table games win and slots win. Rooms revenue increased 4% in 2017 compared to 2016 related to an increase in", "bbox": [56.3, 1092.2, 1181.8, 1113.0]}, {"text": "REVPAR and food and beverage revenue increased 6% in 2017 due in part to an increase in catering and banquets during the year.", "bbox": [56.3, 1116.2, 1148.5, 1137.0]}, {"text": "Non-operating Results", "bbox": [81.8, 1164.1, 270.0, 1184.9]}, {"text": "Interest expense. The following table summarizes information related to interest on our long-term debt:", "bbox": [107.3, 1212.0, 977.9, 1232.9]}, {"text": "Year Ended December 31,", "bbox": [827.3, 1261.5, 1061.2, 1282.4]}, {"text": "2018", "bbox": [763.6, 1287.6, 805.3, 1308.4]}, {"text": "2017", "bbox": [923.0, 1287.6, 964.7, 1308.4]}, {"text": "2016", "bbox": [1082.8, 1287.6, 1124.5, 1308.4]}, {"text": "(In thousands)", "bbox": [893.5, 1312.5, 995.0, 1329.2]}, {"text": "Total interest incurred........................................................................................", "bbox": [55.5, 1333.8, 701.6, 1354.6]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [718.7, 1333.8, 729.1, 1354.6]}, {"text": "821,229", "bbox": [782.5, 1333.8, 850.2, 1354.6]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [878.2, 1333.8, 888.6, 1354.6]}, {"text": "779,855", "bbox": [941.9, 1333.8, 1009.6, 1354.6]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [1037.5, 1333.8, 1048.0, 1354.6]}, {"text": "814,731", "bbox": [1102.0, 1333.8, 1169.8, 1354.6]}, {"text": "Interest capitalized ........................................................................................